14:01.589 --> 14:02.714
(CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS)

14:04.130 --> 14:06.464
-RALPH: Terry's?
-YUNIS: Indeed.

14:06.547 --> 14:08.631
It's the same one we caught
on the surveillance tape

14:08.714 --> 14:10.464
after he changed clothes
at the strip club,

14:10.547 --> 14:11.881
and at the train station
in Dubrow.

14:11.964 --> 14:14.881
Yeah, but there could be more
than one belt buckle like that

14:14.964 --> 14:16.214
-in the world.
-No doubt.

14:16.297 --> 14:18.381
The lab had Maitland's dabs
on file,

14:18.464 --> 14:19.798
matched them up right away.

14:19.881 --> 14:23.047
But here's the thing:
Some were very well defined...

14:24.130 --> 14:26.047
but others... take a look.

14:27.172 --> 14:31.506
See how faint the lines
and whorls are on those?

14:31.589 --> 14:34.547
While on these, they're almost
entirely broken up.

14:36.297 --> 14:37.255
The tech who did the work

14:37.339 --> 14:38.506
said the weaker prints
were like

14:38.589 --> 14:40.464
the prints of an old person.

14:40.547 --> 14:42.631
So, maybe somebody
80 or 90 years old.

14:44.172 --> 14:45.130
So, someone else?

14:45.214 --> 14:47.798
No. They're all the same person.

14:49.798 --> 14:52.381
I asked him if maybe they could
seem blurred because Maitland

14:52.464 --> 14:54.381
was moving fast, wanting
to change clothes quick

14:54.464 --> 14:56.047
to get out of town. He said no.

14:56.130 --> 14:58.089
Did you check them against
the ones in the van?

14:58.756 --> 15:00.381
Indeed.

15:00.464 --> 15:02.881
The well-defined ones were
an easy match.

15:02.964 --> 15:04.130
But here's the thing.

15:04.214 --> 15:07.214
Originally, we IDed five sets
of prints.

15:07.297 --> 15:10.506
Terry's, the kid Merlin's,
the van's owner in New York,

15:10.589 --> 15:12.547
-his wife and his daughter.
-Okay.

15:12.631 --> 15:14.089
But there was one set...

15:14.172 --> 15:16.464
we thought was too degraded
to bother with.

15:17.422 --> 15:18.631
So, take another shot,

15:18.714 --> 15:21.339
compare them against the old man
prints on the belt buckle.

15:22.047 --> 15:23.547
YUNIS: Buckle. Van.

15:23.631 --> 15:25.172
Terry strong. Terry degraded.

15:25.255 --> 15:27.839
Terry young. Terry ancient.

15:30.547 --> 15:33.547
What's happening here?
I've...

15:33.631 --> 15:36.714
Maybe hold that question
until I'm done.

15:36.798 --> 15:37.714
(CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS)

15:37.798 --> 15:39.839
We also found this.

15:39.923 --> 15:42.047
-(CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS)
-RALPH: What is it?

15:42.130 --> 15:44.089
YUNIS: At first,
we thought it was semen,

15:44.172 --> 15:45.339
but it's not.

15:45.422 --> 15:48.172
Besides, semen doesn't do this.

15:49.339 --> 15:51.130
-RALPH: The same stuff?
-They're 90 percent sure.

15:51.214 --> 15:52.422
And there's more of it

15:52.506 --> 15:54.964
-in other parts of the barn.
-Was anyone working there?

15:55.047 --> 15:57.964
Maybe it's motor oil,
engine lubricant.

15:58.047 --> 16:01.089
-They tested for that.
-How about livestock salve?

16:01.172 --> 16:02.547
Um... Udder liniment?

16:02.631 --> 16:04.964
-You know, bag balm?
-Tested for that, too.

16:05.047 --> 16:07.756
-So, what is it?
-Well, they're still testing.

16:11.964 --> 16:13.255
I think we should go and...

16:14.756 --> 16:16.923
contact Howie Saloman,
Alec Pelley,

16:17.005 --> 16:19.547
-bring them in on this.
-Why would we do that?

16:20.422 --> 16:21.631
Just let them know
what's going on.

16:21.714 --> 16:23.422
Yeah, but we don't know
what's going on.

16:24.547 --> 16:26.673
Exactly, so... Yeah.

16:27.839 --> 16:29.881
See if they have
any bright ideas.

16:33.881 --> 16:35.214
(KEYS RATTLE)

16:36.631 --> 16:38.422
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

17:08.005 --> 17:10.506
(SCHOOL BELL RINGS)

17:10.589 --> 17:12.714
THERESA OGLETREE: Mrs. Maitland,
this is not your girls' fault

17:12.798 --> 17:15.130
in the least,
please understand that.

17:15.923 --> 17:17.422
But the kids in school...

17:19.464 --> 17:22.798
There's a growing hostility
towards Maya and Jessa,

17:22.881 --> 17:25.005
and I'm afraid that it's only
going to escalate.

17:25.089 --> 17:27.047
Can't their teachers
protect them?

17:27.756 --> 17:28.673
Can't you?

17:28.756 --> 17:30.923
This is coming from
the parents as well.

17:31.005 --> 17:32.547
So, they're being expelled?

17:32.631 --> 17:35.631
-"Expelled" is the wrong word--
-Okay, well let me think.

17:36.714 --> 17:39.381
How about we just say
they're on sabbatical?

17:39.464 --> 17:40.964
Yes, I like that much better.

17:41.047 --> 17:42.881
You have to understand
my position.

17:42.964 --> 17:44.047
I do understand.

17:44.130 --> 17:45.673
You have to look out for
the welfare of

17:45.756 --> 17:48.214
all of the students and not just
the ones who are being

17:48.297 --> 17:50.130
harassed and bullied. I get it.

17:53.297 --> 17:54.798
I can help you find a school...

17:55.506 --> 17:56.464
but I am afraid wherever

17:56.547 --> 17:58.547
-the girls enrol--
-Got it.

17:58.631 --> 18:00.172
Maybe you can consider
home schooling?

18:00.255 --> 18:02.297
I can certainly help you
with that.

18:03.089 --> 18:04.589
And mother to mother?

18:04.673 --> 18:06.798
I think it's outrageous when
children have to pay

18:06.881 --> 18:08.255
for the sins of a parent.

18:10.089 --> 18:11.172
Sins?

18:12.631 --> 18:13.964
My husband was innocent.

18:20.339 --> 18:21.381
HOWIE SALOMAN:
What do you mean

18:21.464 --> 18:23.089
the state lab
doesn't know what this shit is?

18:23.172 --> 18:24.756
It's the state lab
for Christ's sake.

18:24.839 --> 18:26.130
YUNIS: They're working on it.

18:26.214 --> 18:27.589
ALEC PELLEY: And they're sure
all the prints are Terry's?

18:27.673 --> 18:29.422
-The van and the buckle?
-YUNIS: They are.

18:29.506 --> 18:31.589
HOWARD: Sounds to me like
you're still trying to nail him.

18:31.673 --> 18:32.964
RALPH: No, Howard, we're just--

18:33.047 --> 18:34.964
