my time's my own.

18:41.339 --> 18:44.089
HOWARD: So, now it's all about
getting justice for Terry, huh?

18:44.172 --> 18:46.839
RALPH: Uh...
For Terry, for Frankie Peterson.

18:46.923 --> 18:48.923
But, Howard,
I'm not gonna get to do that

18:49.005 --> 18:50.464
for either of them.

18:50.547 --> 18:53.673
