maybe even the kids, but...

19:59.506 --> 20:02.255
Yeah, but they weren't
with Maitland around the clock.

20:02.339 --> 20:04.964
-That's right.
-(RALPH INHALES DEEPLY)

20:05.464 --> 20:06.673
I don't know.

20:06.756 --> 20:09.130
I guess I could fly up there
for a couple of days myself,

20:09.214 --> 20:11.339
but I don't think
that's enough time.

20:11.422 --> 20:14.673
I have a State Police Homicide
conference in Atlanta tomorrow.

20:14.756 --> 20:16.506
HOWARD:
How about sending Holly Gibney?

20:19.381 --> 20:20.464
Holly Gibney.

20:21.589 --> 20:23.005
Yeah, the one and only.

20:23.964 --> 20:25.130
